{"tid":1682861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［招募］抗爭塗鴉。","createTime":"2019-10-30T10:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T21:19:12.000Z","uid":154039,"like":57,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"7cb3da9f9fb6897a93a6de6106c1abb11781a418","tid":1682861,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:10:33.000Z","msg":"手足好，即使今日我哋對街頭抗爭嘅方向和成效有所迷惘，對每次每次目睹手足被壓在地上怒不可遏，<span style=\"color: orange;\">我哋《塗鴉手冊》仍然想用行動去做好本份，堅持落去，直至最終勝利。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">《塗鴉手冊》正在籌劃出一份實體手冊</span>，10-12頁，用例子簡述塗鴉抗爭的 1)理論 2)技巧 3)備忘，讓我們在（至少）這一範疇上有更深刻的理解和共識；手執噴墨時，一橫一竪當中都有所動機與意義。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">第一版《塗鴉手冊》期待能在兩星期後（10/11/2019）出版，並在抗爭現場免費派發。</span>（成本所限，預計只印製50份，限定派予『正在噴油的手足』）另外，也會公開Online PDF。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">Freedom is not free.</span> 當我哋著手籌備《塗鴉手冊》出版時，希望讀到這一句的你，也能夠收拾心情，為香港找一個崗位。<br />\n<br />\n我哋現在急切需要以下人選，如果恰巧你或你的朋友有興趣，我們共同努力，一齊試，一齊做！<br />\n<br />\n招募崗位：<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">文字編輯、校對</span><br />\n- 出版、印刷<br />\n<br />\n招募投稿：<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">照片：任何塗鴉作品</span>（附上拍攝日期和地點）<br />\n- 文字：新手教學、裝備概覽<br />\n- 意見、建議、投稿（無限）<br />\n<br />\n招募聯絡/ 查詢：<a href=\"https://t.me/Karamazov2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FKaramazov2019&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt31UwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=8c68295c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Karamazov2019</a><br />\n<br />\n（歡迎任何有相關經驗 或 抱有一股熱誠的手足。歡迎任何詢問 / 推薦 😃）<br />\n<br />\n另外歡迎加入我們的Telegram。<br />\n公佈板：<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEq5U76pjKvzTrbYjg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAEq5U76pjKvzTrbYjg&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt31UwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=5773c818\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEq5U76pjKvzTrbYjg</a><br />\n討論區：   <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/IXoPohcGUuEN6vJ8Q9SL_g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FIXoPohcGUuEN6vJ8Q9SL_g&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt31UwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=d7bc2b04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/IXoPohcGUuEN6vJ8Q9SL_g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">沒有大台的運動之所以成功，當然是因爲我們每一個也在參與！塗鴉，反抗！</span>"},{"pid":"0dc05646e93f2d438d7e0790570f19a6910a285d","tid":1682861,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:10:50.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"037ab056aeb8affe4b37ffc905891bb5bd8ac127","tid":1682861,"uid":187796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:13:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b713d7a3cd95cd83c62c83920dea2477c1570d87","tid":1682861,"uid":24467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:13:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5dbab913a3d23ff5650f7c53fc7518e3cfbeece1","tid":1682861,"uid":310355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:14:09.000Z","msg":"p牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59abcb19b4faa0990ae6cdac6fad68b0c2bd602","tid":1682861,"uid":6537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:14:10.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c0612bdbd8f625cb96ad6e4220338a6f3ad036","tid":1682861,"uid":171259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:14:38.000Z","msg":"Help push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285e1ef132c5df9d701d21303beb5fed9a66ea30","tid":1682861,"uid":104086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:14:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f4