崗位。<br />\n<br />\n我哋現在急切需要以下人選，如果恰巧你或你的朋友有興趣，我們共同努力，一齊試，一齊做！<br />\n<br />\n招募崗位：<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">文字編輯、校對</span><br />\n- 出版、印刷<br />\n<br />\n招募投稿：<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">照片：任何塗鴉作品</span>（附上拍攝日期和地點）<br />\n- 文字：新手教學、裝備概覽<br />\n- 意見、建議、投稿（無限）<br />\n<br />\n招募聯絡/ 查詢：<a href=\"https://t.me/Karamazov2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FKaramazov2019&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt31UwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=8c68295c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Karamazov2019</a><br />\n<br />\n（歡迎任何有相關經驗 或 抱有一股熱誠的手足。歡迎任何詢問 / 推薦 😃）<br />\n<br />\n另外歡迎加入我們的Telegram。<br />\n公佈板：<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEq5U76pjKvzTrbYjg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAEq5U76pjKvzTrbYjg&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt31UwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=5773c818\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEq5U76pjKvzTrbYjg</a><br />\n討論區：   <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/IXoPohcGUuEN6vJ8Q9SL_g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FIXoPohcGUuEN6vJ8Q9SL_g&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt31UwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=d7bc2b04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/IXoPohcGUuEN6vJ8Q9SL_g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">沒有大台的運動之所以成功，當然是因爲我們每一個也在參與！塗鴉，反抗！</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:17:23.000Z","msg":"有冇興趣做ebook 我可以幫手"},{"pid":"5d4b72dc6ac6865f5240c1f4da9d5403c8902e22","tid":1682861,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee49481ad634f570df45bf37b27e4bad988d4f62","tid":1682861,"uid":223799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7cb3da9f9fb6897a93a6de6106c1abb11781a418","tid":1682861,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:10:33.000Z","msg":"手足好，即使今日我哋對街頭抗爭嘅方向和成效有所迷惘，對每次每次目睹手足被壓在地上怒不可遏，<span style=\"color: orange;\">我哋《塗鴉手冊》仍然想用行動去做好本份，堅持落去，直至最終勝利。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">《塗鴉手冊》正在籌劃出一份實體手冊</span>，10-